      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for the discerning enthusiast, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an uncompromising standard, its condition is beyond reproach, mirroring its original showroom presentation. Every detail reflects a commitment to excellence, offering a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of such impeccable pedigree. We invite serious inquiries to experience a standard of quality that transcends the ordinary.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
